</ref>
* [[Plutonium-Uranium Extraction Plant]] / [[PUREX]] Plant - extracted useful material from spent fuel waste (also see the [[PUREX]] article)<ref name="atli"/><ref name="Gerber2001"/>
* [[Plutonium Recycle Test Reactor]] (PRTR) - experimented with alternative fuel mixtures<ref name="LiniRogers"/><ref name="Gerber2001"/>
